Lines.Comment: To himself, a little woozy
Warning his enemy.
What a bore.
I thought I was done suffering fools.
Still just a child...
The boy king. The Legion does not spare children.
Your father was a good man, Anduin. One of the best.
I will ALWAYS watch over you, my son. No matter what.
Anduin, my son... you've grown.
Soon all will serve. - Serve
I can offer you unlimited power. - Arrogant
Together our victory is assured.
It gladdens my heart to see you once more, friend.
Treacherous Alliance dog. Get in my way, and I'll cut you down.
Well well! Look who it be!
C'mon let's go bust a few heads, eh?
Watch closely, and you might learn something from me.
This will be a fun battle. I can tell!
Terror shall reign!
A new soul to corrupt? Excellent.
This alliance is a glorious one indeed. Let us march onward to victory!
It is good to fight beside you, friend.
Well met, warrior! Let us charge the field of battle together!
I'm not from the future, I'm in the present! I think?
You might be a little too into this righteousness thing. You still have a lot to learn about these realms.
I don't recognize you from any of the battles I've seen. Are you new here?
You're rather nice... for a hero.
What are you staring at?
<laughter> Such delusion.
The honor is all mine, friend.
Well met, friend!
For the Alliance!
Glory to the Alliance!
Do you think it's a coincidence that we are allies? You will be turned.
Bow to the Burning Legion.
As if talking to a dog.
You're one of the few around here I trust, you know.
If I am to accept help, then I am glad it comes from you.
For the Alliance!
My people owe the alliance a great debt
Those who wield the light must be unyielding, lest they burn away.
Hm, you are unworthy of the scarlet crusade.
Making small talk.
ALL THAT YOU HOLD DEAR EXISTS ONLY TO BURN.
BOW BEFORE THE FIRELORD.
